                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I was in the second floor room, right oppo<lb></lb>site the house—the houses are level with one another—they are only two stories high—I saw the prisoner quite plain—it is a flat roof—Draper's-place is a small place, it is only about nine feet wide—the prisoner appeared to be ripping the lead up.</p>
